			padding: 10px 20px;
			border-radius: 15px;
			font-size: 14px;
			background: #007bff;
			color: white;
			border: none;
			margin-left: 10px;
			cursor: pointer;
			transition: all 0.3s ease;
		}

		/* Effet de hover pour le bouton envoyer */
